Class InMemoryCompanyRepository

Object
InMemoryCompanyRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
CompanyRepository
public class InMemoryCompanyRepository extends Object implements CompanyRepository
in-memory implementation of CompanyRepository used for runtime storage without writing to disk keys are stored in lowercase for case-insensitive matching
